data.description: Nestled in sought after NEISD, this traditional home boasts maximum square footage and charming curb appeal. You are greeted by a spacious open floor plan and soaring ceilings that seamlessly connect the living room, kitchen, and breakfast nook. The family room is adorned with a stunning stone fireplace, creating a cozy focal point that exudes warmth. French doors allows natural light to fill the family room while also providing easy access to the backyard. The kitchen features a spacious island that serves as a common gathering space while entertaining or hosting gatherings. Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample counter space finish-off the kitchen. All bedrooms are conveniently located on the second floor, with the primary bedroom offering a sizable sitting room and en suite bathroom. Outside you will be delighted with an extended wooden deck waiting for you to enjoy the beautiful Texas weather. The spacious yard provides endless opportunities for outdoor activities and gatherings. Don't miss out on the chance to make this our own backyard oasis. With easy access to some of San Antonio's major highways and some of its most noted attractions, this home is a must see! Schedule a showing today and be one step closer to making this your next dream home!
